normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d26fc87eb68e757e863af29a16ed6087cc5b1cf","tid":696072,"uid":6962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:42:41.000Z","msg":"以前日日都夢到<br />\n呢排好啲<br />\n一星期兩次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d83d4a521c728f926f69dab7f687145189ab424","tid":696072,"uid":6962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f70a9b0079b40981c91b5ad785a514685f7e9d3","tid":696072,"uid":63449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"以前佢未搵返我 一個月2-3次啦<br />\n搵返我之後 屌 變左一星期4-5次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:44:00.000Z","msg":"你又犯賤既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88464dfcf9c39ca3765f30929f202ba03e69734","tid":696072,"uid":70350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"樓主散咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"d91c5f8e681360a8e62a90c9f479d408e6458feb","tid":696072,"uid":128849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:57:50.000Z","msg":"有啊 分手一年半<br />\n前幾日夢到佢同我係架旅遊巴度和好仲一齊去食飯<br />\n醒返都仲回味緊返工都識笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實已經冇fd做，仲好清楚知道佢對我冇曬感覺只係當我一件曾經好鍾意既玩具，仲要將我地啲嘢周圍唱講到我有幾衰佢有幾hurt<br />\n<br />\n如果夢可以唔醒就好啦"},{"pid":"7a449609503155f8d4d722f74349d66258af0551","tid":696072,"uid":146881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想講 被傷得太深 <br />\n心理陰影真係可以大到不斷發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初時夢見佢對我好差（同現實發生過嘅事一模一樣）<br />\n到後期 反而夢見佢對我好<br />\n（例如送我返屋企 而佢現實從來都未試過）<br />\n每次醒都發現自己喊緊<br />\n我覺得夢見對我好 係我想係夢入面<br />\n實現我一直想佢做嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再後來我識咗新男友<br />\n有一日夢見ex對我好好 <br />\n但我醒起自己已有男友<br />\n就衝咗出去<br />\n佢追出黎 <br />\n送咗本diy相冊寫好多回憶<br />\n話佢愛我 佢好後悔<br />\n我係夢入面喊得好慘 講咗句「太遲啦⋯⋯」就醒咗<br />\n醒完最痛係 你記起 <br />\n對方從未講過佢愛自己，<br />\n亦從未肯同我影一張合照，又哪來相整diy相簿呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到尾 個夢實現咗我對佢嘅最後一個期望：「後悔無及時愛我」<br />\n而最神奇係自從個夢<br />\n我就無再夢見佢...<br />\n可能我潛意識明白到 同佢之間 <br />\n即使係夢境中都無可能一齊...<br />\n但夢唔發 依然係間唔中諗起佢個心乸住乸住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe07566071598fba488e46b8072bdb1b20f5092","tid":696072,"uid":55350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T19:47:23.000Z","msg":"一、兩個月一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想再夢到"},{"pid":"4fea8b24effbef61ee605b763f673e02dac132e1","tid":696072,"uid":12415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T21:14:51.000Z","msg":"尋晚見完佢，之後真係block咗佢，再同朋友直落玩咗一晚，希望以後唔好再夢見佢"},{"pid":"81017d42b18a990804eace367dea402bbdba35d0","tid":696072,"uid":19567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:43:54.000Z","msg":"我琴晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發夢 夢到一齊去園遊會 係一直以嚟嘅夢想...<br />\n始終夢想只可能係夢"},{"pid":"7537112fef377d5e215a7709675662539fcf97fd","tid":696072,"uid":103797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:51:48.000Z","msg":"我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ca61d1161ac636201307fee167f63a8843dd45","tid":696072,"uid":21615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:13:10.000Z","msg":"每次瞓醒都喊"},{"pid":"245918c7cb61c70b320a8a8137385f5e13dfd08f","tid":696072,"uid":157084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"會，而家冇初初咁密，一兩個月一次到，每次個夢都唔同但佢係夢入面都係做d仆街野<br />\n<br />\n利申：散左9年完全冇見過冇聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bde7fa880872ff92d2f49b192dc2d5322cff7d","tid":696072,"uid":6397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1431f5657e14ffe860cc966481480dac9fad5d5","tid":696072,"uid":24812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"前一排同ex終於斷晒聯絡，但一直放唔低<br />\n直到前幾日夢見佢同我講佢同返ex一齊，一向都唔想夢境<br />\n直到今日 我發現到原來佢真係同返ex一齊<br />\n我: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時第六感唔信都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcec666224ac8ce9488ef5bd25966e2dca7e3c5","tid":696072,"uid":4709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T21:42:07.000Z","msg":"5年<br />\n近排佢add返我ig<br />\n<br />\n我都結左婚喇，唔想諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb48e70f93b621678e6b3266d2431c792d87d022","tid":696072,"uid":190633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"晚晚都夢見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢晚晚都同第二條仔打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就晚晚個心都仲痛緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb6b5b6dc79aa64933a93e0c85a0a1a1a5bfe72","tid":696072,"uid":7604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:29:58.000Z","msg":"一醒返唸起已經分左手 嗰種失落感真係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcac4e49bc718693a0b38ddc28908f645c4290d","tid":696072,"uid":138713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply